This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as semantic dependency parsing. The use of deep neural architectures and multitask learning also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the mention of bidirectional-LSTM and multi-layer perceptron suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision) as these are commonly used in image processing tasks.
